Your Privacy

We use cookies and similar technologies on our Site as outlined below. You can use this tool to change your cookie preferences at any time.

We also use cookies to serve personalised advertisements on third-party websites within our network by using a process called real-time bidding. Some personal information (including your IP address and browsing behaviour) may be shared with social media providers, advertisers, analytics and other third-party service providers.

For more information on how we use cookies, see our Cookie Policy or for general information about how we use your personal data, see our Privacy Policy.

Essential Cookies

Always Active

These cookies are strictly necessary to provide you with services available through the Site and to use some of its features, such as access to secure areas. They perform functions like: Ensuring our Site’s pages load quickly; and Preventing any fraudulent payment activity.

Functional Cookies

Always Active

These cookies enable us to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation for you. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our Site. They perform functions like: recommending similar products for you based on the products added to your online shopping bag; recommending sizing of products for you based on measurements you have provided; and allowing you to begin a live chat session with one of our customer services representatives and/or in-store sales associates.

Analytics Cookies

Always Active

These cookies help us understand how our Site and tools on the Site are being used. They help us: understand how effective advertising and marketing campaigns are; and customise and improve our services and user experience on the Site.

Advertising Cookies

These cookies are used to deliver advertising messages more relevant to you, including on third party platforms such as Google, Facebook and Instagram. They perform functions like: preventing the same advertisement from continuously reappearing; identifying whether you purchase products on our Site after viewing our advertisements; and displaying advertisements that are based on your interests. We may also use data derived and collected from tools on our Site in order to support and enhance how we personalise our services for you.
